title: Pro Line® Series Automatic Toasters | KitchenAid
description: The KitchenAid Pro Line® series 2- and 4-Slice Automatic Toasters feature an automatic lift, seven shade settings, a keep-warm function and much more. They deliver a premium performance with a timeless design inspired by the iconic Stand Mixer.
